name: RTCPeerConnection.onicecandidateerror
description: The RTCPeerConnection.onicecandidateerror property is an EventHandler which specifies a function which is called to handle the icecandidateerror event when it occurs on an RTCPeerConnection instance. This event is fired when an error occurs during the ICE candidate gathering process.
